                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.01/47: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-27T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 27, 1931—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>31. Your 82, July 27, noon. Department concurs in the view that no recognition of
                    new Chilean Government is necessary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
